  "S02madadh_u:160": "namo 'stu buddhānāṃ bhagavatāṃ svāhā /",
  "S02madadh_u:161_0": "[7] asyāṃ khalu rāhula mahādaṇḍadhāraṇyāṃ vidyāyām antaśo 'ṣṭottaraśatapadānāṃ sūtraṃ",
  "S02madadh_u:161_1": "granthiṃ baddhāyāṃ hastena dhāryamāṇāyāṃ kaṇṭhena dhāryamāṇāyāṃ samantād yojanaśatasya",
  "S02madadh_u:161_2": "rakṣā kṛtā bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02madadh_u:162": "gandhair vā puṣpair vā mudrābhir vā naiva manuṣyo vāmanuṣyo vābhibhaviṣyati /",
  "S02madadh_u:163": "na viṣaṃ na śastraṃ na rogo na jvaro na prajvaro na vidyāmantro na vetāḍaḥ /",
  "S02madadh_u:164": "na vyādhau nāgnau na viṣodakena kālaṃ kariṣyati /",
  "S02madadh_u:165": "vidyāmantraprayogānāṃ ca sarveṣāṃ sādhuprayuktānāṃ ca bandhanī /",
  "S02madadh_u:166": "parabandhānāṃ ca pramocanī /",
  "S02madadh_u:167": "sarvarogaśokavighnavināśanakarī /",
  "S02madadh_u:168": "kalikaluṣapraśamanakarī /",
  "S02madadh_u:169": "sarvagrahavimocanakarī /",
  "S02madadh_u:170": "yo graho na muñcet",
  "S02madadh_u:171": "saptadhāsya sphuṭen mūrdhā arjakasyeva mañjarī /",
  "S02madadh_u:172": "vajrapāṇiś cāsya mahāyakṣasenāpatir vajreṇādīptena samprajvālitena ekajvālībhūtena dhyāyitvā mūrdhānaṃ sphoṭayet /",
  "S02madadh_u:173": "catvāraś ca mahārājāno 'yomayena cakreṇa kṣuradhārāprahāreṇa vināśayeyuḥ /",
  "S02madadh_u:174": "tasmād yakṣalokāc cyavanaṃ bhavet /",
  "S02madadh_u:175": "aḍakavatyāṃ rājadhānyāṃ na labhate vāsam /",
  "S02madadh_u:176": "[8] asyāṃ khalu rāhula mahādaṇḍadhāraṇyāṃ vidyāyāṃ sakṛtparivartitāyāṃ rājacaurodakāgniviṣaśastrāṭavīkāntāraparvatadurgamadhyagataḥ sarvabhayebhyaḥ pratimucyate /",
  "S02madadh_u:177_0": "iyaṃ khalu mahādaṇḍadhāraṇīvidyā ekanavatigaṅgānadīvālikāsamair buddhair bhāṣitā",
  "S02madadh_u:177_1": "bhāṣyate bhāṣiṣyate ca siddhā paramasiddhā sarvadevanāgayakṣagandharvāsuragaruḍakinnaramahoragābhir",
  "S02madadh_u:177_2": "vanditā sarvajanagaṇaparivṛtā /",
  "S02madadh_u:178": "sarvabhayopadraveṣu mama sarvasattvānāṃ ca śivam ārogyaṃ bhavatu /",
  "S02madadh_u:179": "[9] idam avocad bhagavān āttamanā āyuṣmān rāhulo bhagavato bhāṣitam abhyanandann iti /",
  "S02madadh_u:180": "[10] āryamahādaṇḍadhāraṇīśītavatī samāptā /"
}